---
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import "./styles/index.css";
---

<!-- src/pages/about.astro -->
<Navbar />
<div class="sign">
  <img src="/Union.svg" alt="" srcset="" />
</div>
<div class="wrapper">
  <div class="page-title">Our Story</div>
  <div class="about-hero-section">
    <div class="our-story-text">
      Every great idea begins with a spark-a flicker of inspiration. But turning
      that dream into reality can be challenging. At Ordnungskraft, we
      understand the frustration of having a vision without the tools to bring
      it to life. We've been there, facing the unknown. Ordnungskraft was built
      on the belief that every business, no matter its size, can achieve
      greatness through the power of technology. We've seen how a single
      software solution can transform a company and even reshape industries. Our
      approach is simple yet powerful: we listen. We listen to your aspirations,
      challenges, and dreams, then craft bespoke software solutions tailored to
      your business. We don't just meet expectations; we exceed them. Our
      clients are our partners in innovation. We celebrate their successes,
      learn from challenges, and grow together. From startups to established
      enterprises, we've collaborated with visionaries from all walks of life.
      We've watched our software empower businesses to streamline operations,
      connect with new audiences, and achieve remarkable growth. But our
      greatest reward is seeing the spark in our clients' eyes as their vision
      comes to life through the solutions we build together. This is the story
      of Ordnungskraft-a story of passion, collaboration, and excellence. And
      it's a story we invite you to be a part of.
    </div>
    <a href="/contact"> <button> Schedule a call today </button></a>
  </div>
  <!-- <div class="full-width about-us-mobile">
    <img src="/mobile.svg" alt="" />
  </div> -->
  <div class="full-width about-us-desktop">
    <object data="/desktop-au.svg" type="image/svg+xml"></object>

    <!-- <img src="/desktop-au.svg" alt="" /> -->
  </div>
</div>
<Footer />

<style>
  .sign {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 70px;
    z-index: -1;
  }
 

  .about-hero-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 40px;
    padding-left: 28%;
    padding-right: 5%;
    justify-content: end;
    .our-story-text {
      font-size: 22px;
    }
  }
  .full-width {
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: -400px;
    object {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    body{
      background-color: red !important;
    }
    .full-width {
    margin-top: 00px;
    object {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
    .about-hero-section {
      padding-left: 12%;
    }
    .our-story-text {
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .page-title {
      margin-left: 8%;
    }
    object {
      margin-top: -100px;
    }
  }
</style>
